  "content":"Kevin Trenberth, a distinguished scholar and climate scientist, recently wrote an article for The Conversation on how record ocean heat content is a key factor in the current wet weather that faces New Zealand every summer.\nRead to the full article here: NZ is again being soaked this summer – record ocean heat helps explain it\n"},{
