  "tags": "",
  "content":"Jasmin is the leader of the Earth Sciences New Zealand glider team.\nObserving the ocean is what Jasmin does best. She has been operating autonomous underwater gliders for ten years around Aotearoa New Zealand and around the world. When not at work you can find Jasmin connecting with the moana through waka ama.\n"},{
